attributes.title: I had to pee on my phone because I hated it so much
attributes.review: This is a terrible period tracking app.😡🤬👎 I could not track my period 😓No matter what I did. It was really hard. It’s honestly pretty 🤮stupid it just kept showing this like orange peel 🤢🍊on my screen and I tried like swiping to get away but it would just like stay there. It was also like really racist so that’s really gross 🤮🤢and just all around a bad time. 😤I suggest other period Tracking apps 🧚‍♂️❤️such as “ period tracker” “Flo” or “clue.”Honestly anything is better than this. 🧟‍♂️If you use like an actual calendar to track your period would be better👍. Or maybe you could just stick your fingers up there every once in a while to check, ✌️which I know might sound weird to some but it’s better than using this app because it’s terrible in every way shape and form. To be honest I might throw away my phone and go get a galaxy or some type of Samsung 🤢android something even though I know the quality will be terrible but as long as they don’t have this app on the App Store I will be perfectly fine. In the end I did find a use for this app which is peeing on.💧 If you pee on this app it actually works so just pee 🏊‍♂️on at everyone and hopefully the App Store pees on it too thank you and good night.

attributes.title: Thoughts from Karen Smith 🇺🇸👩🏼🗽🏌🏼‍♀️🍔🦮👨‍👩‍👧‍👧
attributes.review:
I was so excited to downloaded the app to read all the news of our orange🍊 and bigo-... I mean handsome, 💇🏼totally not racist, not misogynistic president:) I could not handle the excitement so I texted 88022 for what I thought might be notifications from Donald J Trump. I wrote a lovely message to Trump about how I lOvE his idea to stop Covid-19 testing and his other plan to send Gen Z back to school because Lord knows we need them gone ☠️😻 But as soon as I hit send I heard a voice that said, “Stupid dishwasher👿Go make me a sandwich!”🗣 I was offended ! I have a maid who cleans and cooks perfectly🤚🏼 I screamed, “ Who was that!” I was not expecting an answer but my iPhone 11 pro max with a MAGA lock screen and Confederate flag case from Home Goods shut off, and the voice came back! “ I’m your FBI Agent you useless Woman.“ I was so shocked as this was an invasion of my privacy! I than went to the app to give it all a second chance but as soon as I clicked on it my phone shocked me! I was electrocuted!🤕 🔌 I was so upset that I went to go do my favorite activity to calm down, harass innocent genius liberals on twitter. However, this only made me more upset because gen z used facts against my statements in which I used my only comeback, “Maga 2020🇺🇸.”😢 In all, this app is a danger to all! Use this app at your own risk!😵

Yeah❤️Anyways, stream FDT by Yg featuring Nipsey Hussle!( It’s a great Christian Song💕) 

Don’t forget to vote red on November 4th!😹

❌❌❌ NOT maga ❌❌❌

 ACAB💋
